com.thomsonreuters.ema.access

Interface Payload


  • public interface Payload
    Payload conveys the data part of item image.
    Payload contains objects of complex type.

      • dataType

        int dataType()
        Returns the DataType of the contained data. Return of DataType.DataTypes.NO_DATA signifies no data present in Payload. Return DataType.DataTypes.ERROR signifies error while extracting content of Payload.
        Returns:
        data type of the contained object
